04:28.206 --> 04:31.896
But what it is is
an enslavement, one

04:31.896 --> 04:34.448
of craving and compulsion.

04:35.931 --> 04:40.172
And if you let it, it'll drag
you even deeper into despair.

04:41.689 --> 04:42.724
Let's open up to you.

04:44.827 --> 04:45.724
Scott please.

04:48.862 --> 04:51.103
- My name's Scott,
and I'm addict.

04:52.310 --> 04:54.586
I haven't had a drink
for about five months.

04:56.965 --> 05:00.793
