05:09.896 --> 05:13.103
And thanks to the
people in this very room

05:15.310 --> 05:18.758
and the support of my loving
wife, I'm gonna stay clean.

05:18.758 --> 05:19.586
Thanks.

05:22.034 --> 05:23.344
- Jacob.

05:28.103 --> 05:30.655
- My name's Jacob,
and I'm an addict.

05:34.103 --> 05:35.827
That's all I have to say.

05:37.344 --> 05:39.275
- You've been coming
here awhile now,

05:39.275 --> 05:40.931
maybe give it some push.

05:40.931 --> 05:41.758
- Some push?

05:41.758 --> 05:42.586
- Just a wee bit.

05:43.551 --> 05:44.413
I'm your sponsor.

05:44.413 --> 05:45.482
You need to trust me.

05:53.172 --> 05:56.206
- My name is Jacob,
and I'm an addict.

05:59.068 --> 06:02.379
I know that when I let it
take over I become powerless.

06:04.413 --> 06:07.068
And like our great speaker
said, we have a problem.

06:09.517 --> 06:13.000
But that problem binds
us, brings us together.

06:16.344 --> 06:20.000
