06:50.689 --> 06:52.000
- The night before
she went missing.

06:53.137 --> 06:54.034
- That's what Raymond said.

06:54.034 --> 06:55.965
- Hi my name's Frank.

06:55.965 --> 06:57.068
I'm an alcoholic.

06:57.068 --> 06:58.275
- It just doesn't make sense.

06:58.275 --> 07:01.586
