07:04.758 --> 07:07.586
- Called me a drunk,
and said I needed help.

07:08.758 --> 07:10.862
- You didn't really
know Jackie that well.

07:12.000 --> 07:14.344
She'd only been coming
here a couple of months,

07:14.344 --> 07:17.448
and the last time she was
seen she was in a pub.

07:17.448 --> 07:18.275
What does that tell you?

07:18.275 --> 07:19.413
- It tells me nothing.

07:21.000 --> 07:22.724
Lots of alcoholics
go in pubs and clubs,

07:22.724 --> 07:24.965
it doesn't mean
they're drinking.

07:24.965 --> 07:27.551
You run that bar
for Christ's sake.

07:27.551 --> 07:29.034
- But I'm going to
prove 'em wrong.

07:29.034 --> 07:30.758
- Russell you're not
a policeman anymore.

07:30.758 --> 07:32.034
This isn't your case.

07:33.413 --> 07:36.827
All we can do is hand out
fliers and help with the search.

07:36.827 --> 07:37.862
- Ridiculous.

07:39.172 --> 07:40.758
Somebody must know something.

07:43.896 --> 07:48.482
- Russell, you
became an alcoholic

07:48.482 --> 07:49.517
because of your job.

07:49.517 --> 07:50.344
- So?

07:53.103 --> 07:55.310
- Forgive me for only
thinking about myself,

07:56.517 --> 07:59.344
but I don't want my
sponsor, my support

07:59.344 --> 08:03.620
