habits and old lifestyles.

08:05.655 --> 08:07.206
It could be bad for both of us.

08:10.241 --> 08:12.206
- A search has been
launched for a woman

08:12.206 --> 08:14.137
who's been reported
missing from her home

08:14.137 --> 08:15.896
on the South side of Glasgow.

08:15.896 --> 08:18.724
32 year old Jacqueline
Crawford was last seen

08:18.724 --> 08:21.413
outside Murray's
Bar on Shuttle Lane

08:21.413 --> 08:24.586
at around two p.m. on
Tuesday the third of January.

08:24.586 --> 08:26.413
Miss Crawford's colleagues
raised the alarm--

08:26.413 --> 08:27.620
- Tell me something.

08:27.620 --> 08:28.586
- When
she failed to turn up

08:28.586 --> 08:29.793
