problem unlike yourself.

08:57.103 --> 08:58.793
- Oh, touche barman.

09:00.620 --> 09:03.482
- Her friend
Antony spoke about the search.

09:03.482 --> 09:04.931
- Paul, Tuesday?

09:06.620 --> 09:07.620
