12:33.620 --> 12:35.724
- Why are you helping me?

12:37.103 --> 12:39.413
- Helping others gives me peace.

12:58.655 --> 13:00.620
- Jacob, let me in.

13:00.620 --> 13:02.068
I need to talk to you.

13:02.068 --> 13:03.379
- Do you want me to leave?

13:04.379 --> 13:07.724
- Not at all.

13:15.896 --> 13:17.068
- Good evening, Russell.

13:18.275 --> 13:19.965
Please come in.

13:32.724 --> 13:36.000
- Strange company to be
keeping this time of night.

13:36.000 --> 13:36.862
