24:52.965 --> 24:56.862
Look I have been on the
street for four years.

24:56.862 --> 24:58.275
I don't need your pity.

24:58.275 --> 25:01.586
So as soon as my clothes
are dry, I'll get away,

25:01.586 --> 25:02.827
and you can get on
with your project.

25:02.827 --> 25:04.413
- I don't pity you.

25:06.448 --> 25:08.000
